isation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage"},{"pid":"855d6fc8d774d6ad412374d437b422ab8b02b3ff","tid":1388663,"uid":287320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:10:55.000Z","msg":"自推 唔好餓親"},{"pid":"7b05ab6035bd6737922f2d9b494d6f08ed2e2c8b","tid":1388663,"uid":162981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:13:59.000Z","msg":"17萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f3df281b0660e645b449b53b04a6fcf44aa6d1","tid":1388663,"uid":287320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b05ab6035bd6737922f2d9b494d6f08ed2e2c8b","tid":1388663,"uid":162981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:13:59.000Z","msg":"17萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:15:20.000Z","msg":"真係用黎買gear就好 餓親事小 爆頭事大"},{"pid":"38d10cf0aed4bf4f793c3ebf50607a988a5ec710","tid":1388663,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:18:19.000Z","msg":"有17萬，買裝備可以救番唔少人，無防具之後好多後遺症醫藥費好甘"},{"pid":"904014cb7aa68b144eb5028b10b5f0001eaf672c","tid":1388663,"uid":42929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:35:06.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e29a364c9fa22120003a19786047c902f9d5a05d","tid":1388663,"uid":287320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:42:24.000Z","msg":"自推 唔好餓親"},{"pid":"c133c322e3b2f98553dcd8e99ae5fe415b54c8be","tid":1388663,"uid":287320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:34:22.000Z"